    {
      "id": "/page/1/Text/1",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">enables one to examine how the dynamic optimization of the informed trader affects the evolution of liquidity over time. The general conclusion is that the informed trader spreads his/her trades over time in a manner that has the effect of smoothing liquidity intertemporally. We return to this issue in the final paragraph.</p>",
      "page": 316,
      "polygon": [
