    {
      "id": "/page/1/Text/316",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">5. The equilibrium informed trades are of order <math display=\"inline\">dt</math>. This reflects the fact that the desired trades of a patient anonymous trader are optimally executed in small pieces.</p>",
      "page": 316,
      "polygon": [
        [
